   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "29.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "31.200", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die bis heute leiden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "31.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "33.480", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und viele trauernde Angeh\u00f6rige, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "33.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "35.800", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "denen unsere Sympathie, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "35.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "38.480", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "unser Respekt und unser Mitgef\u00fchl gelten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "38.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "38.920", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich glaube, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "38.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "43.160", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das sollten wir in diesem Hohen Haus deutlich zum Ausdruck bringen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "43.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "49.200", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "In den letzten Monaten ist viel \u00fcber das Fehlverhalten von Beh\u00f6rden gesprochen worden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "49.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "49.880", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es ist richtig, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "49.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "54.360", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass der demokratische Rechtsstaat das konsequent aufarbeitet, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "54.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "55.480", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "weil wir die Pflicht haben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "55.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "59.720", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "daraus zu lernen und die Dinge zu verbessern."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "59.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "60.680", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber es ist auch richtig, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "60.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "62.600", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn uns entgegengehalten wird, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "62.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "68.640", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass bislang viel zu wenig \u00fcber die Opfer gesprochen wurde. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "68.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "77.720", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir m\u00fcssen in unserem Land eine Kultur der Begleitung der Opfer entwickeln und sie in den Mittelpunkt unserer Rechtspolitik stellen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "77.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "79.600", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deswegen ist es richtig, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "79.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "84.200", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass wir hier weitere Verbesserungen auf den Weg bringen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "84.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "84.880", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir wissen nicht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "84.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "86.320", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "meine Damen und Herren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "86.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "90.080", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ob und wann uns wieder ein Terroranschlag heimsuchen wird. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "90.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "91.280", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir tun alles daf\u00fcr, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "91.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "93.160", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "um dies zu verhindern; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "93.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "96.080", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
